snippet.title: Occupational Therapy Assistant Graduate - Amber Elhard Sand
snippet.description:
Visit PMI.edu - http://bit.ly/2RCKKMm Amber wasn't feeling satisfied in her role in human resources and decided to go into the occupational therapy assistant program at our Denver campus after her mom told her about the field.
